rComments: Best professor I have had by far. Renée is extremely inspiring and is passionate about translation, teaching, and life. She is passionate and knows how to be engaging. A master in the field, and the most relatable professor I have ever had. I also learnt a lot, if you are reading this, thank you for all that you do.

Incredible professor! She is passionate about translation and made class a fun atmosphere. You can tell she has a lot of experience, and she puts it to good use. She also brought desserts to class often, which is always nice! All in all, amazing prof. Best I've ever had.

This professor is fantastic. She makes the course material fun and very applicable to the current job market. Classes with Renee are an asset, and you come away with great skills! She also provides plenty of feedback for improvement.

GREAT PROF! She uses "real-world" knowledge and doesn't sugar coat and say that anyone can be a good translator. In this intro class, her teaching will clearly help you figure out whether you really are interested in translation or not. I am in the translation program and looking forward to my next class with her!!!

Best Prof I've ever had. Super passionate about what she's teaching, and possesses a really awesome sense of humour (and style!). The perfect age to be relatable (and use social media to her advantage) yet informative and can provide real-world knowledge. EXTREMELY organized and helpful. The kind of prof that makes you want to be a good student.
